            <h2 class="font-serif text-5xl italic mb-12 text-[#1b1c1a]">Quick Questions & Local Details</h2>
            <div class="space-y-0">
              
              {/* FAQ 1 */}
              <details class="group border-b border-[#d2c5b3]/30 py-6 cursor-pointer [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1b1c1a] outline-none">
                  Can I store luggage in the village?
                  <span class="text-[#785611] text-xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300">+</span>
                </summary>
                <p class="text-[#4e4538] text-sm leading-loose mt-4 pr-8">
                  No, Frigiliana does not have lockers. If arriving early, please store luggage at the ALSA station in Nerja or in Málaga city before heading up.
                </p>
              </details>
              
              {/* FAQ 2 */}
              <details class="group border-b border-[#d2c5b3]/30 py-6 cursor-pointer [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1b1c1a] outline-none">
                  Can I drink the tap water?
                  <span class="text-[#785611] text-xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300">+</span>
                </summary>
                <p class="text-[#4e4538] text-sm leading-loose mt-4 pr-8">
                  The public water supply is standard. Uniquely in Frigiliana, AMARA has a central water softening system, making the water much more pleasant for showering and washing. For drinking, however, many guests still prefer the taste of bottled water.
                </p>
              </details>
              
              {/* FAQ 3 */}
              <details class="group border-b border-[#d2c5b3]/30 py-6 cursor-pointer [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1b1c1a] outline-none">
                  Do I need a car in Frigiliana?
                  <span class="text-[#785611] text-xl group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform duration-300">+</span>
                </summary>
                <p class="text-[#4e4538] text-sm leading-loose mt-4 pr-8">
                  While not strictly necessary, we recommend a car for the flexibility to explore Andalusia. Important to know: The historic core (where AMARA is located) is pedestrian-only. You will park at the public parking garage at the village entrance and walk up.
                </p>
              </details>
              
              {/* FAQ 4 */}
              <details class="group border-b border-[#d2c5b3]/30 py-6 cursor-pointer [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
                <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1b1c1a] outline-none">
                  How far is the beach?
